{"tid":862362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成班傻閪整基建搵美國佬","createTime":"2018-10-14T18:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T19:10:20.000Z","uid":104830,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d909d604ad21fed2bac5cad3f5f5d225568df49","tid":862362,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"整基建搵美國佬<br />\n不如下次叫雞帶埋老婆去<br />\n成班傻撚尻獨條撚立咩<br />\n個撚個都去食譚仔飲咩撚尻喜茶<br />\n用塗寶,支負寶<br />\n最撚關心就係隻700<br />\n所以香港算尻吧啦<br />\n心繁支那的香港人<br />\n共享大支那榮耀<br />\n成班七頭喺度聽埋啲咩撚貓貓一齊叫<br />\n算撚數啦<br />\n香港啲靚仔都做撚曬支那狗<br />\n瞓下覺冇咁嬲啦<br />\n香港已經玩撚猿<br />\n香港過強國口岸多撚到數唔曬<br />\n出街個撚個都條強國喱<br />\n香港已經係支那一部份<br />\n怪就怪啲廢老<br />\n趕撚走左英國佬"},{"pid":"7a0938fdd1eb650afb645f33ad37dbd612115df3","tid":862362,"uid":13038,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:58:14.000Z","msg":"樓主都係其中一個支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a9e3b601be1ecc20c4faa1a3d02cdb54bab077","tid":862362,"uid":104830,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:04:15.000Z","msg":"你企係度就唔會填咩<br />\n嗨撚大左?"},{"pid":"4fc22d1bb5cdb8d17d337162e62d1a46a7a08b60","tid":862362,"uid":187076,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:07:44.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - lambigloser"},{"pid":"0788caa3b561f2471daa15ea3869943fc5d8896d","tid":862362,"uid":104830,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4fc22d1bb5cdb8d17d337162e62d1a46a7a08b60","tid":862362,"uid":187076,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:07:44.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - lambigloser"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:10:20.000Z","msg":"block你老母閪呀 死廢青"}]}